descriptionHtml:
Tired of normal Bethesda intro? Need a good gameplay refresher? Look no further. I got you covered!

[color=#ffff00]Installation
[/color]Make sure to backup your videos folder in your Skyrim/Data folder. This replaces them. So PLEASE back them up. Im not guaranteed you will like this. Or that it has anything to do with skyrim.
